de_fedra_autumn Fedra is a village set in the mountains, and as the name states, in autumn. The counterterroists' spawn is around and in a small house that is near bombspot A and a stretch away from B. The terrorists spawn point is on the other end of the village, equidistant to A and B. The layout of this map is inspired by that of Dust2, otherwise having no other resemblences. There are: - 64 Player-spawns - 2 Bombspots - radar map in bsp - soundscapes - 3d skybox with moving clouds - use of hint/ skip texture and areaportals render-time: 1 min 52 sec Optimized, balanced and tested with and for 64 Players on the Sachsenkneipe servers. Special thanks to www.sachsenkneipe.de for testing and improving it! Sachsenkneipe XL - 64 Slots: 193.192.58.170:27015 Enjoy playing it :) wostok
